How it Works
 ->The API Request: The script sends a "GET" request to a URL. The server responds with a JSON object (a dictionary in Python).
 ->The Loop: The while True loop keeps the script running indefinitely.
 ->The Wait Time: time.sleep(30) is crucial; if you ping a server too many times per second, they will block your IP address.



